setType

void setType(String type)
Sets the xsi:type attribute for the element. Note that this basically adds a new attribute called "type" in the "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" namespace - it doesn't automatically declare this namespace with the "xsi" prefix. If the xsi prefix is declared with declarePrefix(String, String) method on this element or any higher elements, it this will come out as xsi:type.

Parameters:
type - The type, as a string.

namespace - The namespace URI, as a String.
